Transform your dental routine with the state-of-the-art Philips Sonicare 4100 Power Toothbrush! This rechargeable electric toothbrush harnesses the revolutionary Sonicare technology that removes up to 3x more plaque than a manual toothbrush. Brushing has never been easier, as its built-in smart timer ensures you brush for the dentist-recommended 2 minutes, while its advanced pressure sensor protects your gums from over-brushing and preventing gum recession. With a sleek, ergonomic design, this toothbrush offers a comfortable grip and maneuverability around every nook and cranny of your smile. Upgrade to the superior cleaning power and convenience of the Philips Sonicare 4100 Power Toothbrush – the ticket to a brighter, healthier smile! Includes 1 electric toothbrush, 1 SimplyClean (C1) brush head, and 1 USB charger.
